%%%CALL
%%%VALGRIND
%%%DESCRIPTION Running without arguments
%%%OUTPUT
ERROR in Fraud2 parameters. Not enough arguments
Run with the following arguments:
Fraud2 <K> <minSeed> <maxSeed> <inputFile.loc> 

Parameters:
<K>: an integer with the number of clusters to use in the K-means algorithm
<minSeed>: an integer with the minimum seed value to use
<maxSeed>: an integer with the maximum seed value to use
<inputFile.loc>: name of the location file
